    "narrative_summary": "Archer-Daniels-Midland Company reported first quarter 2024 financial results, showing adjusted segment operating profit of $1,317 million and adjusted EPS of $1.46. The company affirmed its full-year adjusted EPS guidance range of $5.25 to $6.25. Results were impacted by lower pricing and execution margins, particularly in the Ag Services and Oilseeds segment, while improvements in input costs and volume contributed positively to earnings."
